The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are: cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI.

- cs.CL (Computation and Language): This sub-category deals with natural language processing and generation, which is the main focus of this paper. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval): This sub-category deals with techniques for retrieving relevant information from large datasets, which is relevant to the task of generating questions from reviews. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): This sub-category deals with various machine learning techniques, which are used in this paper for generating questions. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): This sub-category deals with various AI techniques, which are used in this paper for generating questions. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks): This sub-category deals with various social and information networks, which are relevant to the task of generating questions from online reviews.
